# Reverse-proxy /p/demo/* to the 1context-demo Pages project. Lets us
# show the wiki at haptica.ai/p/demo/ without grafting it into the
# SvelteKit build (the wiki has its own assets, anchor links, .md
# companions, etc — far cleaner kept as a self-contained Pages project).
# 200 = rewrite (URL bar stays on haptica.ai), 301 = redirect.

/p/demo            /p/demo/                                  301
/p/demo/           https://1context-demo.pages.dev/          200
/p/demo/*          https://1context-demo.pages.dev/:splat    200
